{"type": "article", "id": 2233, "title": "带天篷的床", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:24:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222259IQZC5ytc1ioHpSRj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">设计工作室 Joseph Walsh 为了在英国查特斯沃思庄园举办的“Modern Makers“ </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">展览所设计的 Canopy Bed（带天篷的床），不同于传统的是张床并没有四根立柱来搭起篷子，而是利用流线型的木质结构挑起了纱幔，看上去舒适随意，仿佛有音乐在流动。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135127Zu6g0LM18eRjOGoc.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"361\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135127EnD2e7bQrXmxYLw0.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"361\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}